Definition: a chronic skin disease characterized by dry red patches covered with scales
Example: occurs especially on the scalp and ears and genitalia and the skin over bony prominences
Synonyms: skin_disease, a, chronic, skin, disease, characterized, by, dry, red, patches, covered, with, scales, occurs, especially, on, the, scalp, and, ears, genitalia, over, bony, prominences
Category: noun.state
